des:
Visiting San Diego, California? Learn about attractions and fun things to do in our beautiful city.

To get started, enable the skill and say "Alexa, open San Diego Guide".

Or say "Alexa, ask San Diego Guide..."
- for an attraction
- what should I do
- for the news
